item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】ALAC - Isa TKM & Isa TK+ (Nickelodeon OST) [ALAC 16Bit/44.1kHz]
item.description:
Isa TKM/+ is a successful Nickelodeon telenovela broadcasted in Latin America, Spain, Portugal, Italy, Israel, Slovenia and the U.S. trough Nickelodeon & MTV Tr3s.
Isa TKM was also a pop group that toured in Latin America and the U.S., they received many gold and platinum records in Brazil, Mexico, Argentina, Venezuela and Colombia​



Their group title means “Isa, I Love You So Much/ Isa ILY” the second season of Isa was titled Isa TK+ meaning “Isa, I love you more” & Nickelodeon had plans to make a third season titled “Isa TKF (Te Kiero Full)” Full is a slang word from Venezuela, the place where they come from and where they recorded the first season, this word could translate as “Isa, I Love You Like Crazy/I Love You to the fullest”, but the novela ended with 2 seasons

Isa TKM: LA FIESTA VA A EMPEZAR (The Party Is About to Start) (2008)


Isa TK+: SIGO AL CORAZÓN (I Follow My Heart) (2009)

in this second season, Isa TKM has two new group members

This novela was primarily popular in Brazil, Mexico and Venezuela and it’s Nickelodeon’s 2nd novela from a lot they’ve made, it was the most successful latin Nickelodeon production before “Grachi” from the same producers arrived 2 years later in 2011

in memory of it’s creator Mariela Romero who passed away some weeks ago. may she rest in peace <3
